      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a superlative example of the legendary S54-powered chassis. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, this powerplant delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal mechanical grip. Crucial preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard, including documented rod bearing replacement and professional rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing fresh bushings and high-performance dampers to maintain the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. With zero oxidative degradation on the undercarriage and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
